---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Highland Primary Care"
  description="Privacy policy for Highland Primary Care in Sherman, TX."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-x">
      <div class="prose-medical mx-auto">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>
          <em>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</em>
        </p>

        <p>
          This Privacy Policy describes how Highland Primary Care ("we", "us", "our") collects, uses, and protects information when you visit our website at highlandprimarycare.net or contact our practice.
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Information you provide:</strong> name, email address, phone number, and any other information you submit through our contact or booking forms.</li>
          <li><strong>Automatic information:</strong> IP address, browser type, pages visited, and other standard web analytics data.</li>
          <li><strong>Health information:</strong> Protected health information (PHI) collected during your care is governed by HIPAA and our Notice of Privacy Practices, which is provided at your first visit. This website does not collect PHI.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To respond to your inquiries and schedule appointments.</li>
          <li>To improve our website and services.</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell or rent your personal information. We may share information with service providers who help us operate our website and practice, all bound by confidentiality obligations. PHI is shared only as permitted by HIPAA.
        </p>

        <h2>Marketing & Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          We use Facebook Pixel and standard web analytics tools to understand how visitors use our site and to deliver relevant advertising. You can opt out of personalized ads through your browser settings or via the Network Advertising Initiative (NAI).
        </p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of personal information we hold about you by contacting our office at <a href="mailto:info@highlandprimarycare.net">info@highlandprimarycare.net</a>. Patients have additional rights under HIPAA, detailed in our Notice of Privacy Practices.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          Highland Primary Care<br />
          300 N Highland Ave Suite 455<br />
          Sherman, TX 75092<br />
          Phone: <a href="tel:9038715671">(903) 871-5671</a><br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:info@highlandprimarycare.net">info@highlandprimarycare.net</a>
        </p>

        <hr />
        <p>
          <em>Note: This is a baseline privacy policy. Review with legal counsel before publishing to ensure compliance with all applicable state and federal regulations.</em>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
